<div id="review_460321243" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/460321243" />
    <a title="Mark Hartzer" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7408040-mark-hartzer"><img alt="Mark Hartzer" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1326387102p2/7408040.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/460321243?book_show_action=true">Jun 23, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mark Hartzer" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mark Hartzer" href="/user/show/7408040-mark-hartzer">Mark Hartzer</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer460321243" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7455664377780695312">As much as I liked this book, I can&apos;t give it a full 5 star review because it is too dated. Yes, &apos;holocaust denial&apos; folks are pretty much a fringe idiot band, but that was a long time ago comparatively speaking. There is nothing about global warming whatsoever. Nor is there anything about &quot;Scientology&quot;. <br/><br/>This is not to say this book is not worthwhile. It is. I&apos;m afraid it is difficult to keep up with the various crackpot things with our ratings driven media, but i would enjoy an updated version o</span>
  <span id="freeText7455664377780695312" style="display:none">As much as I liked this book, I can't give it a full 5 star review because it is too dated. Yes, 'holocaust denial' folks are pretty much a fringe idiot band, but that was a long time ago comparatively speaking. There is nothing about global warming whatsoever. Nor is there anything about "Scientology". <br /><br />This is not to say this book is not worthwhile. It is. I'm afraid it is difficult to keep up with the various crackpot things with our ratings driven media, but i would enjoy an updated version of this book very much. </span>
  <a data-text-id="7455664377780695312" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

